


1. Uid- It is used to display the user id from dual table.
        Example: Select uid from dual;

2. User: Used to display the user name from dual table
         Example: Select user from dual;

3. Nvl: It is used in fields where instead of displaying null we can display the zeros.
        Example: select nvl ('salary', 0) from emp;

4.vsize: This function shows number of bytes used for the expression.
         Example: Select vsize('Info tech') from dual;
